"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-schedule-2024-dates-time-b2590185.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Dates and times of all 329 events across 19 days in Paris this summer  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998894964, \"rank\": 1.1037402156064119e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  The 2024Olympicsin Paris officially began with the opening ceremony on Friday 26 July, setting off a two-and-a-half-week festival of sport which comes to an end on Sunday 11 August.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998894964, \"rank\": 1.1037402156064119e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years on fromthe pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games, Paris 2024 will see a new sport,breakdancing (or breaking), added to the mix.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other modern additions like 3x3 basketball, BMX, surfing, skateboarding and climbing all retain their spots in the schedule, but karate and baseball have been dropped.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.24155049022247e-12, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then there are the traditional big draws to watch out for, like swimming (Sat 27 July to Sun 4 Aug), artistic gymastics (Sat 27 Jul to Mon 5 Aug), athletics (Thu 1 to Sun 11 Aug) and track cycling (Mon 5 Aug to Sat 10 Aug).\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With an extra day of swimming on the schedule, it means the middle Olympic weekend will feature swimming, gymnastics and athletics across both days for the first time.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In total there are 32 sports, with some further broken down into separate disciplines making 48 in total.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All together there will be 329 events - and therefore 329 gold medals to fight for.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is a closer look at the full day-by-day schedule for the Games, including every session for every sport:  ***********************************************************************************************************  Archery  Artistic gymnastics  Athletics  Badminton  Basketball  Basketball 3x3  Beach volleyball  Boxing  Canoe slalom  Cycling (road)  Equestrian  Fencing  Football  Golf  Handball  Hockey  Judo  Rowing  Sailing  Shooting  Swimming  Table tennis  Tennis  Volleyball  Water polo  ***********************************************************************************************************  Archery  Artistic gymnastics  Athletics  Badminton  Basketball  Basketball 3x3  Beach volleyball  Boxing  Canoe slalom  Cycling (road)  Equestrian  Fencing  Golf  Handball  Hockey  Sailing  Shooting  Swimming  Table tennis  Tennis  Vol